<h2>Recommended Tech Stack for Performance</h2>
<div class="details-grid">
  <div class="metric-card">
    <div class="metric-title">Frontend Framework: Next.js</div>
    <p class="metric-description">A React-based framework that enables
      server-side rendering (SSR) and static site generation (SSG), leading to
      incredibly fast page loads and excellent SEO performance.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="metric-card">
    <div class="metric-title">Hosting: Vercel or Netlify</div>
    <p class="metric-description">These platforms are built for modern web
      applications, offering global CDNs, automatic deployments, and serverless
      functions that ensure your site is always fast and available.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="metric-card">
    <div class="metric-title">Content Management: Headless CMS</div>
    <p class="metric-description">A Headless CMS (like Sanity, Strapi, or
      Contentful) separates your content from the presentation layer, giving you
      more flexibility and better performance than traditional systems like
      WordPress.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="metric-card">
    <div class="metric-title">Analytics: Google Analytics 4 & Search Console</div>
    <p class="metric-description">These free tools from Google are essential for
      tracking your website's traffic, understanding user behavior, and
      monitoring your search performance.</p>
  </div>
</div>